    "body": "I'm not able to reproduce this problem on Windows 10 with Electron 1.4.15.\r\n\r\nOne possible reason might be that your `authWindow` is not created in the global scope, so it's getting garbage collected. But in that case you'd probably see an error, so I'm not sure.\r\n\r\nCan you try [this branch](https://github.com/zeke/electron-quick-start/commits/issue-8677) and see if the problem exists there?\r\n\r\n```sh\r\ngit clone https://github.com/zeke/electron-quick-start                \r\ncd electron-quick-start \r\ngit checkout issue-8677\r\nnpm install\r\nnpm start\r\n```"
